This is Part 2 of Miranda Cosgrove's favorite episodes of Science Minute. We teamed up with Miranda Cosgrove to make Science Minute with MinuteEarth, an illustrated segment for her TV show: Mission Unstoppable. If you like this, there's a ton more over at  @CBSUnstoppable  or, if you're in the US, watch the new season on CBS on Saturday mornings!
